Package: bvars
Type: Package
Title: Estimation and forecasting of bayesian VAR models
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: person("Joerg","Rieger",email="joerg.rieger.jr@gmail.com",role=c("aut","cre"))
Description: This package estimates bayesian VAR models. The user can choose between several priors (e.g., Minnesota or Uninformative prior).
    It also has functions to calculate and plot IRF-models, forecasts, and Forecast Error Variance Decompositions.
License: GPL-3
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.0)
Imports:
    MASS,
    gridExtra,
    ggplot2,
    ggfortify,
    pracma,
    extraDistr
Suggests:
    doParallel,
    foreach,
    parallel,
    knitr
URL: https://github.com/joergrieger/bvars
BugReports: https://github.com/joergrieger/bvars/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
